title.narrative: PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for Support to National Policies for Urban Poverty Reduction

description.narrative: This activity (PROCOFSERVICES and P0053 for Support to National Policies for Urban Poverty Reduction) is a component of Support to National Policies for Urban Poverty Reduction reported by FCDO, with a funding type of 'Procurement of Services' and a budget of £6,668,784. This component benefits India, and works in the following sector(s): Public sector policy and administrative management, Decentralisation and support to subnational government. , with the following implementing partners: Deloitte Touche Tohmatsu India LLP, ICF Consulting Services Ltd. The start date is 22-04-2009 and the end date is 30-06-2015.
